I"ü<div class="p">Cry fire! cry fire! the world is amok,</div>
<div class="p">As it plunges abrupter than a falling rock,</div>
<div class="p">As it bobs its tail skyward as a diving duck,</div>
<div class="p">As it hurtles apace screaming, "whee!"</div>
<p>Â </p>
<div class="p">Cry fire! cry fire! we enter a spin,</div>
<div class="p">A lapel pin a-rattling in a rusty tin,</div>
<div class="p">Or a whirling machine with a dreadful din,</div>
<div class="p">Or a terrier bit by a flee.</div>
<p>Â </p>
<div class="p">Cry fire! cry fire! the world is grotesque,</div>
<div class="p">In proportion appears as a low burlesque,</div>
<div class="p">Or a paunchy proportion not statuesque,</div>
<div class="p">Or a fertile and rank potpourri.</div>
<p>Â </p>
<div class="p">Cry fire! cry fire! we must act with haste,</div>
<div class="p">Or with freshets of fire is the earth lain waste,</div>
<div class="p">And with fervor of tears do we mourn the past,</div>
<div class="p">And at grief's vigil cry out, "Oh me!"</div>
